PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Kenneth J. Bourque, of Cambridge Narrows, New Brunswick, as director of the board of directors of the Saint John Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective May 18, 1992, in the place of Fernand Lanteigne, whose term will expire.
